metadata.BenchmarkMetadata.NAME: Isaac ROS DecoderNode Benchmark
metadata.BenchmarkMetadata.CONFIG:
ros2_benchmark_config:
  additional_fixed_publisher_rate_tests:
  - 10.0
  - 30.0
  - 60.0
  assets_root: /workspaces/isaac_ros-dev/ros_ws/src/ros2_benchmark/assets
  benchmark_duration: 5.0
  benchmark_mode: BenchmarkMode.LOOPING
  benchmark_name: Isaac ROS DecoderNode Benchmark
  benchmark_namespace: r2b
  binary_search_acceptable_frame_loss_fraction: 0.05
  binary_search_acceptable_frame_rate_drop: 10.0
  binary_search_duration_fraction: 1.0
  binary_search_terminal_interval_width: 10.0
  cpu_profiling_interval_sec: 1.0
  custom_report_info:
    data_resolution: Resolution(1920, 1080, Full HD)
  default_config_version: 0.30.0
  default_service_future_timeout_sec: 15.0
  enable_cpu_profiler: true
  enforce_publisher_rate: false
  input_data_end_time: -1.0
  input_data_path: datasets/r2b_dataset/r2b_compressed_image
  input_data_start_time: -1.0
  linear_scan_acceptable_frame_loss_fraction: 0.01
  linear_scan_acceptable_frame_rate_drop: 5.0
  linear_scan_duration_fraction: 1.0
  linear_scan_step_size: 5.0
  load_data_in_real_time: false
  log_file_name: kpi.json
  log_folder: /output
  monitor_info_list:
  - calculators:
    - class_name: BasicPerformanceCalculator
      config:
        report_prefix: ''
      module_name: ros2_benchmark.basic_performance_calculator
    service_name: start_monitoring0
  play_messages_service_future_timeout_sec: 15.0
  playback_message_buffer_size: 1
  publish_tf_messages_in_set_data: false
  publish_tf_static_messages_in_set_data: false
  publisher_lower_frequency: 10.0
  publisher_upper_frequency: 600.0
  record_data_timeline: false
  revise_timestamps_as_message_ids: false
  set_data_service_future_timeout_sec: 60.0
  setup_service_client_timeout_sec: 20.0
  start_monitoring_service_timeout_sec: 10
  start_recording_service_future_timeout_sec: 35.0
  start_recording_service_timeout_sec: 30
  test_iterations: 5
